race.comment: NEWTON HAYZE (5) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 1 (30.69). Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. The form from his last run stacks up well. Can continue the winning form. COOL IT (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (36.04) in a Grade 5 at Q Parklands. Leading chance. PROFESSOR STARR (3) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won two of four starts. Missed the frame latest (31.01) when fourth over 550m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. WEATHER REPORT (2) can sneak into the finish again.
